1
00:00:01 --> 00:00:06
Welcome to the spoken tutorial on <b>Installation of Scilab on Windows operating system</b>.

2
00:00:07 --> 00:00:12
I will install <b>Scilab</b> version 5.2 on <b>windows operating system</b>.

3
00:00:13 --> 00:00:19
This procedure is applicable to all versions of Scilab and other versions of windows operating system.

4
00:00:20 --> 00:00:24
You can download scilab from the scilab.org website.

5
00:00:25 --> 00:00:30
Go to the Products, select <b>Download</b> and click.

6
00:00:31 --> 00:00:40
Scroll down, click on <b>scilab 5.2</b> under the <b>Windows</b> section .

7
00:00:41 --> 00:00:44
This will open a dialog to download the exe file.

8
00:00:45 --> 00:00:49
Click on Save File, the downloading will start.

9
00:00:50 --> 00:00:53
It will take few minutes. I will minimize this.

10
00:00:54 --> 00:00:57
Minimize the browser.

11
00:00:58 --> 00:01:02
The direct link to download page is as shown.

12
00:01:03 --> 00:01:09
Before starting the installation process please make sure that your computer is connected to the internet.

13
00:01:10 --> 00:01:15
It is required to download and install <b>Intel Math Kernal Library</b> .

14
00:01:16 --> 00:01:17
I will minimize this.

15
00:01:18 --> 00:01:24
Double click on the <b>scilab Setup</b> file to start the installation procedure.

16
00:01:25 --> 00:01:27
Click <b>Run</b>.

17
00:01:28 --> 00:01:32
<b>Select set up language</b> as <b>English</b>, click <b>OK</b>.

18
00:01:33 --> 00:01:36
This will start the <b>Scilab Setup Wizard</b>.

19
00:01:37 --> 00:01:38
Click Next to continue.

20
00:01:39 --> 00:01:41
Accept the license agreement, click Next.

21
00:01:42 --> 00:01:46
Select a destination folder to install scilab on your computer.

22
00:01:47 --> 00:01:49
Click Next.  Go for <b>Full Installation</b>.

23
00:01:50 --> 00:01:51
Click Next.

24
00:01:52 --> 00:01:54
Next. Next.

25
00:01:55 --> 00:01:57
Click Install to start the installation.

26
00:01:58 --> 00:02:02
Click OK to give the internet connection permission.

27
00:02:03 --> 00:02:10
This will start downloading of Intel Math Kernal Library for Scilab.

28
00:02:11 --> 00:02:19
This will take few minutes.

29
00:02:20 --> 00:02:27
Downloading of Intel Math Kernal Library has completed and the installation procedure for scilab has started.

30
00:02:28 --> 00:02:45
This will take few minutes.

31
00:02:46 --> 00:02:50
Installation of scilab has completed. Click "Finish".

32
00:02:51 --> 00:02:59
This will Launch Scilab 5.2 on your computer.

